commit.message:
Minor changes in tree-vrp.c

gcc/ChangeLog:

	* tree-vrp.c (dump_asserts_for): Print loc->expr instead of
	name.
	(extract_code_and_val_from_cond_with_ops): Verify that name is
	either cond_op0 or cond_op1.

From-SVN: r238762
